00:20:19,442 --> 00:20:23,665
A game like Vainglory and any other MOBA for that matter really relies on fast networking

358
00:20:23,725 --> 00:20:28,528
and high quality networking. Part of the challenge is that you're always going to be playing

359
00:20:28,548 --> 00:20:33,851
on either Wi-Fi or LTE. Nobody plugs in their phone to like a fixed line network, which

360
00:20:33,911 --> 00:20:37,133
means that if you think about competitive gaming, would you play a competitive PC game

